    "id": "cloche-c4z",
    "title": "Run context store: CLOCHE_RUN_ID env var, context.json, cloche get/set",
    "description": "Every step in a workflow (host and container) needs the cloche run ID available as an environment variable (e.g. CLOCHE_RUN_ID) so steps can locate their .cloche/\u003crun-id\u003e/ directory. Add a context.json file in that directory that acts as a key-value store shared across steps. Add 'cloche get \u003ckey\u003e' and 'cloche set \u003ckey\u003e \u003cvalue\u003e' CLI commands that read/write context.json, using the CLOCHE_RUN_ID env var to find the right file. This eliminates the need to constantly pass metadata between steps via JSON output mappings.",
